name: 2nd International Conference on the Emerging Technologies in Computing
content: The International Research Conference is a federated organization dedicated to bringing together a significant number of diverse scholarly events for presentation within the conference program. Events will run over a span of time during the conference depending on the number and length of the presentations. With its high quality, it provides an exceptional value for students, academics and industry researchers.
organizers: Institute For Engineering Research and Publication (IFERP)
